# Pipeline API Samples
# Base URL: http://localhost:8000

### 1. Get cheapest route (composite cost)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/route?start_lon=4.711&start_lat=52.3&end_lon=7.205&end_lat=53.2019&cost_type=composite

### 2. Get cheapest route (tariff-optimized)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/route?start_lon=4.711&start_lat=52.3&end_lon=7.205&end_lat=53.2019&cost_type=tariff

### 3. Get cheapest route (shortest distance)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/route?start_lon=4.89&start_lat=52.37&end_lon=5.29&end_lat=52.13&cost_type=distance&max_snap_km=100

### 4. Long distance route (Germany to France)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/route?start_lon=10.00&start_lat=53.55&end_lon=2.35&end_lat=48.85&cost_type=composite

### 5. Find nearest nodes to Amsterdam
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nearest-nodes?lon=4.89&lat=52.37&max_km=20

### 6. Find nearest LNG terminals
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nearest-nodes?lon=5.29&lat=52.13&max_km=500&node_type=lng_terminal

### 7. Find nearest trading hubs
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nearest-nodes?lon=13.40&lat=52.52&max_km=300&node_type=hub

### 8. List all nodes (first 500)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nodes

### 9. List trading hubs only
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nodes?hubs_only=true

### 10. List Dutch pipeline infrastructure
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nodes?country=NL

### 11. List German hubs
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nodes?country=DE&hubs_only=true

### 12. List LNG terminals
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nodes?node_type=lng_terminal

### 13. Get reachable nodes from TTF Hub (within 5 €/MWh cost)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nodes/1/reachable?max_cost=500.0

### 14. Get reachable nodes from a specific node (wider budget)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/nodes/20590/reachable?max_cost=10.0


### 14. Get reachable nodes from a specific node (wider budget)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pipelines/segments

